# Generated / machine-specific artifacts of the Node framework smoke fixtures.
# The committed sources are the driver `.mjs` files + each group's
# `package.json` / `package-lock.json`; everything below is materialised by the
# Python orchestrator (`tests/live/node_frameworks.py`) at run time.

# Installed framework deps — `npm install` per group dir (see node_frameworks.py).
node_modules/

# Symlink to the SDK's native binding, created per group dir so the SDK native
# client loads when a driver runs with cwd = the group dir. Machine-specific.
native/
